| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-5098 — Recovery Inhibition (worldleaks)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 1ac17014-1e2d-5c72-9cc1-5c58b002e266"
